realization of a(t) := u^\\[Dagger] (t) a u(t) for the study quantum \
information scrambling, where a is a local Clifford unitary operator and u(t) \
is a (random) Clifford-type time-evolution operator. For the remaining \
arguments spec, ..., see RandomCliffordCircuit. CliffordScramblingCircuit[k, \
spec, ...] assumes a := Xk, where Xk is the Pauli-X operator on the k^th \
qubit.", "synonyms" -> {}, "tabletags" -> {}, "title" -> 
